                <answer correct=true>al 4-lea</answer>
                <answer>primul</answer>
            </answers>
        </question>
        <question>
            <text>Care este adresa IPv6 corecta, daca pornim de la MAC `6C-3B-B1-EF-7E-38` si parcurgem etapele procesului EUI-64?</text>
            <answers>
                <answer>`6C-3B-B1-FE-FF-EF-7E-38`</answer>
                <answer>`6C-3B-B1-FF-FE-EF-7E-38`</answer>
                <answer>`6E-3B-B1-FE-FF-EF-7E-38`</answer>
                <answer correct=true>`6E-3B-B1-FF-FE-EF-7E-38`</answer>
            </answers>
            <explanation>
                - pas 1: se imapte adresa MAC in 2: `6C-3B-B1`, `EF-7E-38`
                - pas 2: se insereasa secventa `FF-FE` intre cele 2 jumatati
                - pas 3: se modifica bitul 1 din prima secventa a primei jumatati din 0 pe 1
                ```
                6C = 0110 1100 -\> 0110 1110 = 6E
                ```
                
                deci rezultatul e: `6E-3B-B1-FF-FE-EF-7E-38`
            </explanation>
        </question>
        <question>
            <text>Care este adresa IPv6 corecta daca pornim de la adresa MAC `C0-8F-02-52-A3-AA` si parcurgem etapele procesului EUI-64?</text>
            <answers>
                <answer>`C0-8F-02-FE-FE-52-A3-AA`</answer>
                <answer>`C2-8F-02-FE-FF-52-A3-AA`</answer>
                <answer>`C0-8F-02-FF-FF-52-A3-AA`</answer>
                <answer correct=true>`C2-8F-02-FF-FE-52-A3-AA`</answer>
            </answers>
            <explanation>
                - pas 1: se imapte adresa MAC in 2: `C0-8F-02`, `52-A3-AA`
                - pas 2: se insereasa secventa `FF-FE` intre cele 2 jumatati
                - pas 3: se modifica bitul 1 din prima secventa a primei jumatati din 0 pe 1
                ```
                C0 = 1100 0000 -\> 1100 0010 = C2
                ```
                
                deci rezultatul e: `C2-8F-02-FF-FE-52-A3-AA`
            </explanation>
        </question>
